[05/09/2017 10:14:51] <font color="#ffffff">-Patrick.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:14:51] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola, mamá.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:14:53] <font color="#ffffff">-Cuánto me alegra verte.</font>
