[05/09/2017 10:15:41] <font color="#ffffff">-Ya veo.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:15:46] <font color="#ffffff">A mis espaldas.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:15:46] <font color="#ffffff">-Sí.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:15:48] <font color="#ffffff">Más o menos.</font>
