[05/09/2017 10:23:48] <font color="#ffffff">-Eddie.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:23:51] <font color="#ffffff">-No, no te odia.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:23:54] <font color="#ffffff">-Lo he oído, mamá.</font>
