[05/09/2017 10:31:44] <font color="#ffffff">-A ver, héroes,</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:44] <font color="#ffffff">haced cola e id avanzando.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:46] <font color="#ffffff">Que la manduca se nos va a enfriar.</font>
