[05/09/2017 10:31:50] <font color="#ffffff">-Sí que es verdad.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:53] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Ataque!</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:57] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Al suelo! ¡Al suelo!</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:57] <font color="#ffffff">-No.</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:59] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Truman!</font>
[05/09/2017 10:31:59] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Cuidado!</font>
[05/09/2017 10:32:05] <font color="#0000ff">(Explosiones)</font>
